Sentencas: A-site Ba-deficient PrBa1-xCo2O5+delta (PB1-xCO, x = 0-0.08) oxides are synthesized and evaluated as cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs) with respect to crystal structure, chemical stability, thermal expansion behavior, electrical conduction and electrochemical performance.
Titulo: Characterization of Ba-deficient PrBa1-xCo2O5+δ as cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: PB1-xCO with Ba-deficiency x = 0-0.08 has an orthorhombic structure, which shows lattice shrinkage with bigger x; higher Ba-deficiency x=0.1
Titulo: Characterization of Ba-deficient PrBa1-xCo2O5+δ as cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
Characterization of Ba-deficient PrBa1-xCo2O5+δ as cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The PB1-xCO oxides are chemically stable with Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 (GDC) electrolyte at 1050 degrees C in air.
Titulo: Characterization of Ba-deficient PrBa1-xCo2O5+δ as cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Thermal expansion coefficient of PB1-xCO decreases slightly with higher Ba-deficiency.
Titulo: Characterization of Ba-deficient PrBa1-xCo2O5+δ as cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Electrical conductivity of PB1-xCO exhibits an initial decrease with higher Ba deficiency to x = 0.03 and then increases gradually to a maximum at x = 0.08.
Titulo: Characterization of Ba-deficient PrBa1-xCo2O5+δ as cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Introduction of Ba deficiency greatly improves electrochemical performance of PB1-xCO, characterized by decreased area specific resistances (ASRs) with higher Ba deficiency.
Titulo: Characterization of Ba-deficient PrBa1-xCo2O5+δ as cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The ASR values as low as 0.115 Omega cm(2) and 0.093 Omega cm(2) have been obtained at 600 degrees C in air for PB1-xCO with x = 0.05 and 0.08 respectively.
Titulo: Characterization of Ba-deficient PrBa1-xCo2O5+δ as cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: These results have demonstrated that the Ba-deficient PB1-xCO (x = 0.03-0.08) oxides are promising cathode materials for IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: Characterization of Ba-deficient PrBa1-xCo2O5+δ as cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
